 and large icy satellites, but also insights for discussing future observations of exoplanets.},
author = {SOTIN, C and GRASSET, O and MOCQUET, A},
doi = {10.1016/j.icarus.2007.04.006},
file = {:Users/simonlock/Library/Application Support/Mendeley Desktop/Downloaded/SOTIN, GRASSET, MOCQUET - 2007 - Mass–radius curve for extrasolar Earth-like planets and ocean planets.pdf:pdf},
issn = {00191035},
journal = {Icarus},
keywords = {Equation of state,Exobiology,Extrasolar planets,Ices,Terrestrial planets},
month = {nov},
number = {1},
pages = {337--351},
title = {{Mass–radius curve for extrasolar Earth-like planets and ocean planets}},
